      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# Instead of one attention head, we run H heads in parallel.\n",
        "# Each head uses a smaller head_dim = embed_dim / num_heads.\n",
        "#\n",
        "# Why multiple heads?\n",
        "#   Different heads can learn to attend to different kinds of relationships:\n",
        "#   - Head 1: might learn syntactic relationships (subject-verb)\n",
        "#   - Head 2: might learn semantic similarity (synonyms)\n",
        "#   - Head 3: might learn positional proximity\n",
        "#\n",
        "# After all heads produce their outputs, we concatenate them and\n",
